name: Eney'sPlanet 🦟
description:
Hello!

Today i present the first FPS game i worked on using Unity3D.

Eney's planet is a 3D Fps Game where you have to fight giants insects in order to progress to the next level!

I've added few adjustments such as:

  1. Different weapons 
  2. New graphics
  3. More Enemies and spawners
  4. More Health 

Created By:

Arwa Alfuraih <3
